text:
My life's purpose is to use
the education and knowledge

that I have to make a positive
impact on people's lives.

I'm passionate about learning
and continuing to grow,

and I believe that by doing
so I can contribute to making

I want to inspire others to
pursue their goals and dreams,

and I hope to be a role model
for Saudi women and beyond.

Ultimately, my purpose is
to live a meaningful life

and leave a positive
legacy behind.
